verbose_text: RT-qPCR was performed in a CFX96 Real-Time PCR Detection System (Bio-Rad) with 20 muL reaction mixture containing 10 muL of 2 x SYBR pre-mixture (BioTeke, Beijing), 4 muL of diluted cDNA (1:10), forward and reverse primers (0.25 muM), and 5 muL water.
